dup from the mesh,it pulls up easier than you\u2019d expect. \n\nThen I go in with a toothpick around the edges to get out anything stuck (ear wax is sneaky like that). \n\nOne more pass with a clean swab, then I roll up a little Fun Tac and gently press it into the mesh to pull out what the swab and toothpick couldn\u2019t reach.\n\nFor the case, I like to use a cotton swab for the buildup. Pay extra attention to the charging holes so everything keeps working right. \n\nLast step: 70% isopropyl alcohol on a microfiber towel for a wipe down. These things live in your pocket and your bag all day, so they need the disinfect too.\n\nSave this one for your next cleaning day. \u2728", "hashtags": [], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DaiqlE9iU7c/", "commentsCount": 12, "dimensionsHeight": 1080, "dimensionsWidth": 1080, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736074232_18442933195140899_2602647568605162400_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_s1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF7DXD0FQ2twAsLCBY9y7ybN_4Z8o79F2kvfrDNtW5jjixBfsQyLpGInyJr9OyNjZV7tjb_W6oMd9oKBD7QNk77&_nc_ohc=SNZ1Ts8RuDoQ7kNvwE909qS&_nc_gid=3ik3UFbkf0o4kmKTLT7l5A&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQBa-kvRnCJMz_oQG4slO6TeAXKyigrzxZEtpisnhZd13A&oe=6A61ABBD&_nc_sid=bc0c2c", "images": ["https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736074232_18442933195140899_2602647568605162400_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_s1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF7DXD0FQ2twAsLCBY9y7ybN_4Z8o79F2kvfrDNtW5jjixBfsQyLpGInyJr9OyNjZV7tjb_W6oMd9oKBD7QNk77&_nc_ohc=SNZ1Ts8RuDoQ7kNvwE909qS&_nc_gid=3ik3UFbkf0o4kmKTLT7l5A&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQBa-kvRnCJMz_oQG4slO6TeAXKyigrzxZEtpisnhZd13A&oe=6A61ABBD&_nc_sid=bc0c2c", "https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736346376_18442933204140899_962178166553751913_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_s1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_